com.sun.media.jsdt.event

Class RegistryAdaptor

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sun.media.jsdt.event.RegistryAdaptor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RegistryListener, java.io.Serializable, java.util.EventListener

    public abstract class RegistryAdaptor
extends java.lang.Object
implements RegistryListener
    The adaptor which receives Registry events. The methods in this class are empty; this class is provided as a convenience for easily creating listeners by extending this class and overriding only the methods of interest.
    Since:
    JSDT 2.0
    See Also:

        public void connectionFailed(RegistryEvent event)
        invoked if a problem is detected with the connection to the Registry.

        This listener is automatically removed as a listener on the connection that reported the failure, to prevent continual failure notifications.
